<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7466742>
    dc:description "FIGURE 37. Canonical correspondence analysis (CCA) ordination of 7 sampling collections based on physicochemical variables and 41 abundant taxa of caddisflies larvae. Abbreviations: WT = water temperature; NH3 = ammonia-nitrogen (NH3- N). Abbreviations of taxa are shown in Table 3." ;
